OL,3,CConvicted paedophile jailed again for
OL,4,Cpossessing thousands of indecent images
OL,6,FA convicted paedophile has been
OL,7,Freturned to prison after police
OL,8,Fdiscovered thousands of indecent
OL,9,Fimages of children during a routine
OL,10,Fcheck.
OL,12,FGary McVeigh, of Delamere Street, was
OL,13,Fsentenced to 14 months in prison at
OL,14,FChester Crown Court on 6 January.
OL,16,FPolice found a number of indecent
OL,17,Fimages across McVeigh's mobile phone,
OL,18,Fa laptop, a USB stick and a memory
OL,19,Fcard during a routine visit to his
OL,20,Fhome as he was already a registered
OL,21,Fsex offender.
