OL,6,FFurther checks revealed McVeigh
OL,7,Fpossessed more than 12,950 indecent
OL,8,Fimages of children.
OL,10,FThere was also evidence that McVeigh
OL,11,Fdistributed more than 120,000 images
OL,12,Fto other paedophiles.
OL,14,FThe 48-year-old from Winsford had
OL,15,Fpreviously pleaded guilty to
OL,16,Fpossession of an indecent of a child,
OL,17,Fpossession of a prohibited image of a
OL,18,Fchild, possession of an extreme
OL,19,Fpornographic images and three counts
OL,20,Fof making indecent images of children.
