OL,3,CConvicted paedophile jailed again for
OL,4,Cpossessing thousands of indecent images
OL,6,FFollowing the sentencing, Detective
OL,7,FSergeant Helen Wrigley said:
OL,9,F"As a registered sex offender, McVeigh
OL,10,Fwas subjected to a number of vigorous
OL,11,Fchecks on a regular basis to prevent
OL,12,Freoffending and ensure he was keeping
OL,13,Fto his conditions.
OL,15,F"He was well aware of these checks,
OL,16,Fbut despite this he continued to
OL,17,Foffend, downloading and sharing
OL,18,Fthousands of indecent images which
OL,19,Fshowed vulnerable children being
OL,20,Ftortured, raped and abused.
