OL,3,CConvicted paedophile jailed again for
OL,4,Cpossessing thousands of indecent images
OL,6,F"Thankfully, through our effective
OL,7,Fmonitoring, McVeigh was quickly
OL,8,Farrested and is now facing the
OL,9,Fconsequences of his actions.
OL,11,F"I hope it reassures people that we do
OL,12,Fcarefully monitor registered sex
OL,13,Foffenders in the community and take
OL,14,Faction when a breach is discovered."
OL,16,FIn addition to his prison sentence,
OL,17,FMcVeigh was also ordered to pay #187
OL,18,Fcosts and sign the sex offenders
OL,19,Fregister for ten years.
